data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!! Are you looking for a few acres for your own mini farm? You have now found it!! This place would be the perfect fit to bring your dreams to reality!! This 4 bedroom 2 bath brick home is ready for its new owner to come in and love on it and make it their very own. The possibilities are endless. One thing you'll notice when viewing this home is that ALL the rooms are so spacious!! You have not one but two giant rooms for entertaining all your company and the kitchen overlooks the great room so no cooking alone. There are so many possibilities that come with this place but the location and space is a key. This beautiful home is just minutes from I-81 as well as I-77 if you commute for work. Are you a horse lover? This place is also perfect for your horses too as you are close to the New River Trail and within 30 minutes to the horse camps as well. Come take a look, this one won't last long!
